metadata.name: SEAGULL DREAM
metadata.description:
Seagull LEVEARTH
This Is The True Story Of A Lone Seagull Named Levearth. And It Still Continues. 
You'll see the places and friends of Levearth, alone seagull who, after being alone in life, has resumed flying freely and high. This seagull is still wandering and living now. That's why this project will be as long as he lives and will present you the most beautiful visuals as NFT from his own eyes. Please stay with him.

You will watch flying and Istanbul through my eyes. Thank you all. Seagull LEVEARTH
